cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.MM

This paper discusses the challenges of analyzing large-scale video data, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed solution involves edge computing and collaboration between camera nodes, which falls under the categories of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper also discusses the potential improvements in communication bandwidth, which is relevant to multimedia (cs.MM).
